repository-code: "https://github.com/drajb/whisper-local"
url: "https://github.com/drajb/whisper-local"
abstract: >-
  Whisper Local is a free, open-source, fully offline AI dictation tool for
  Windows and macOS. It uses OpenAI Whisper (via faster-whisper) to transcribe
  speech to text at the cursor, with global hotkeys, voice commands, push-to-talk,
  custom transforms, per-app rules, and optional local LLM polish via Ollama.
  No audio or transcript data leaves the user's machine.
keywords:
  - speech-to-text
  - dictation
  - whisper
  - voice-typing
  - transcription
  - privacy
  - offline
  - local-ai
  - accessibility
